widgets_values:
Put the face from Image 1 onto the body in Image 2.
Put Image 1’s face on Image 2’s head.
Replace the black empty space in Image 2 with the face from Image 1.
Make the person in Image 2 have the face from Image 1.

Leave the clothing and color grading exactly the same. Maintain the same facial features from Image 1. Retain the same hair texture from Image 1. Keep the exact same facial expressions from Image 1.

// This is a comment and will be
// ignored. Specify new changes below:
Change to blonde hair.

#### Models

Get the vae and text encoder from [ComfyOrg](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/vae-text-encorder-for-flux-klein-9b/tree/main/split_files)

Get the 9B distilled model from [Black Forest Labs](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-klein-9B/resolve/main/flux-2-klein-9b.safetensors)

#### Need Help?
As always feel free to join and Discord and ask me for help!

[Invite Link](https://discord.gg/hq8qPbvznf)

RECCOMENDED SETTINGS
SIGMA MAX ~0.95-0.98
DO NOT GO HIGHER THAN 1

UNBYPASS LATENT MASK
IF IMAGE CHANGES TOO
MUCH
